                <lb break="yes"/>
                <p>M. de Humboldt @, a<lb break="yes"/>Cl@gyman at Amsterdam, a statement respecting the<lb break="yes"/>population of America, and the numerical amount of<lb break="yes"/>the Catholic@, compared with that of the Protestants.<lb break="yes"/>The total population of America he makes 34,284,000.</p>
