                </table>
                <lb break="yes"/>
                <p>The black population is composed of 1,440,000 free<lb break="yes"/>blacks, and of 5,079,000 slaves. The different @<lb break="yes"/>spoken are @ follows:&#x2014;</p>
                <lb break="yes"/>
                <table>
